@startuml
title Edit Existing Trail Information

actor User
boundary SearchPanel
boundary TrailPanel
control TrailService
database Database

User -> SearchPanel : search/selectTrail(trailId)
SearchPanel -> TrailPanel : openTrailForEdit(trailId)

TrailPanel -> TrailService : getTrailDetails(trailId)
TrailService -> Database : fetchTrailById(trailId)
Database --> TrailService : trail
TrailService --> TrailPanel : trail

TrailPanel --> User : displayEditableTrailForm(trail)

User -> TrailPanel : editTrailFields(updatedInfo)
User -> TrailPanel : clickSaveChanges()

TrailPanel -> TrailService : updateTrail(trailId, updatedInfo)
TrailService -> Database : updateTrailRecord(trailId, updatedInfo)
Database --> TrailService : updatedTrail
TrailService --> TrailPanel : updatedTrail

TrailPanel --> User : displayUpdateConfirmation(updatedTrail)

@enduml
